    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省在关税迫在眉睫的情况下向特朗普推销矿业交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ontario-pitches-trump-on-mining-deals-with-tariffs-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对加拿大北方国家征收高额关税之际，加拿大人口最大省份的领导人正提议与美国在关键矿产方面建立“新的战略联盟”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ontario-pitches-trump-on-mining-deals-with-tariffs-looming</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预算僵局令法国企业陷入不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/french-economy-latest-business-uncertainty-high-due-to-budget-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行表示，法国企业继续面临该国长期预算危机带来的高度不确定性，导致经济前景低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/french-economy-latest-business-uncertainty-high-due-to-budget-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告称，特朗普的关税即将到来，将包括石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
